'''''Flicker and Flames''''' is the debut [[Extended play|EP]] from ''[[The Silents]]''.  It was released on 6 March 2006<ref>[http://www.aria.com.au/pages/ArchivedAustralianReleases-April2006.htm ARIA releases - April 2006]</ref> by Rubber Records through [[EMI]]. The EP was produced by Dave Parkin ([[Red Jezebel]]) and the single, "Nightcrawl" has received significant airplay across [[Triple J]] networks in Australia. 

==Track listing==
All songs written by Benjamin Stowe, Sam Ford, James Terry and Alex Board.<ref name="APRA">[http://www.apra.com.au/site/public/searchworks.stm Australasian Performing Rights Association]</ref>

# "Nightcrawl" - 2:50
# "High Blues" - 3:08
# "Gypsy" - 2:00
# "Night People" - 2:57
# "Mind In A Blanket" - 8:51

